# UI and event rules

- CW frames that behave as dialogs must use the CW modal stack.
- ESC closes the latest CW modal only.
- UI must not block WASD during normal gameplay.
- Search/edit boxes must clear focus correctly and not trigger global delete.
- Carbonite clear during CW sync must not clear the CW queue.
- User Carbonite clear must clear the CW queue.
- On taxi, suppress repeated expensive route rebuilds and repeated Carbonite recentering.
- Taxi route refresh should be throttled and then rerun once after taxi end.
- Transport discovery must avoid spam, duplicates, local overlays, and LFG teleport false positives.
- No/ESC on discovery confirmation must suppress repeats.
- Death autoroute must be optional, delayed/retried, instance-context based, and non-looping.
